{"tid":2289986,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"好好笑:D:D:D #社評","createTime":"2020-11-17T15:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T13:07:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd1c67b5244f6bd1a01fa5e872da13d33893b5c","tid":2289986,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #社評<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201117/2PXHKK3S2ZAKPKPHQYDVIGTAOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201117%2F2PXHKK3S2ZAKPKPHQYDVIGTAOQ%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4yDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=a8ea1ef1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201117%2F2PXHKK3S2ZAKPKPHQYDVIGTAOQ%2F&h=be0caf20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201117/2PXHKK3S2ZAKPKPHQYDVIGTAOQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n經濟封鎖和經濟支持 - 邁克<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ofgd89KKDm015pFmJNtP6AAixkQ=/1125x889/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I32AXCUFRJA3NCFYH5INJE52TA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fofgd89KKDm015pFmJNtP6AAixkQ%3D%2F1125x889%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI32AXCUFRJA3NCFYH5INJE52TA.jpg&h=8dcc6e8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n達明一派fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n搞分化的五毛，七嘴八舌呼籲《蘋果》剷除不撐特朗普的專欄作者，要他們（我們！）一個二個活活餓死。這招毒辣的順我者昌逆我者亡，雖然具濃郁紅衛兵特色，但實行起來肯定奏效，我一聽暗叫弊傢伙，驚到手騰腳震，連續三日三夜瞓唔着覺。八爪魚咁多爪的同文當然定過抬油，檔口摺埋轉行經商又好睇風水又好，不愁沒有其他機會大展鴻圖，除了煮字什麼都做不來的基伯，唯一出路恐怕是跪求鄧達智聘用當另類時裝模特兒，臨老戰戰兢兢步上天橋搵兩餐晏仔。最衰係平日習慣大使，左手來右手去，銀行戶口形同虛設，莫講話隔宿之糧，有時連去美心飲下午茶的閒錢也沒有，傳說的海外幕後金主又無跡可尋，唉，早知有今日，加入紅營搖旗吶喊又點話，真是悔不當初呀。<br />\n<br />\n經濟封鎖的確是最好的懲罰，同樣道理，經濟支持也比精神支持實惠，譬如正在伊館舉行的達明一派演唱會，因法國疫情嚴峻不方便飛回香港捧場，原本十分沮喪，後來聽聞現場有紀念品發售，立即喜上眉梢，急發短訊委託公共秘書余先生代購，總算可以出一分綿力撐志同道合的老朋友。環保袋是必買的，縱使家中堆積如山，多一個不嫌多，tee恤也是指定動作，不過紅底白字的一款太蝦老弱殘兵，自知carry唔到，只好單單要黑底黃字。應運而生的口罩更加非擁有不可，他日武肺成為歷史，這就是具時代意義的產物，有資格擺進博物館做展品。面臨失業也勇往直前小解慳囊，自己都覺得偉大&mdash;&mdash;希望黎老闆念在我這個月有額外開支，暫時不要炒我魷魚吧。"},{"pid":"b539a5919d332a0e2cfb4375d9b66548183b94ff","tid":2289986,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T00:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929274b31d84a2009776e82cec2e892194a5d1ab","tid":2289986,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8074c3692ab1b1088c9170c18a5f2adbccd5603b","tid":2289986,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"講乜鳩？"}]}